 physique peut prendre pour miroir réflexif, l'inventeur du mot énergie, Aristote.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aMechanicsxSources. 0aMechanics. 0aPhysicsxHistory. 0aSciencexHistory. 4aGeneral Physics. 4aHistory of science. 7aSCIENCE / Philosophy & Social Aspects.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759822683423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9782759822683.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK